<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="3Jun1938"><font color="red">3 June 1938</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Viscount Carlow): Well, I am nearly exhausted, working literally night and day &hellip; I received the copies of S.a.s.i.S and they have been greatly admired by all who have seen them &hellip; I am asking my friend Eugene Jolas to send you a copy of the last issue of <i>transition</i> which contains a fragment of W.i.P </div>
